  "original_title": "\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No one has the support of SLN",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena said that the Sri Lanka Freedom Party has decided that it will not vote for any candidate running for the post of President.",
        "The names of Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, Sajith Premadasa, Anura Kumara Dissanayake, Dallas Alahapperuma, Sarath Fonseka have been proposed for the post of new President."
      ],
